# Start Services

## 1. Initialize Database (first time or after schema changes)
```
node src/config/init-db.js
```

## 2. Frontend (port 3000)
```
npm start
```

## 3. Backend (port 3002)
```
node server.js
```

Note: The webpack dev server proxies /api requests to the backend on port 3002.
